@startuml
actor Pembeli
boundary View
control AuthController
entity UserModel
database Database

Pembeli -> View: Buka Halaman Login/Register
alt Sudah punya akun?
    Pembeli -> View: Submit Email & Password
    View -> AuthController: POST /login
else Belum
    Pembeli -> View: Submit Form Registrasi
    View -> AuthController: POST /register
    AuthController -> UserModel: register(data)
    UserModel -> Database: INSERT users
    Database --> UserModel: OK
    UserModel --> AuthController: User object
end

AuthController -> AuthController: Auth::attempt()
alt Valid Kredensial?
    AuthController --> View: Redirect ke Halaman Utama (Session created)
    View --> Pembeli: Tampilkan Dashboard
else Tidak Valid
    AuthController --> View: Redirect back with Errors
    View --> Pembeli: Tampilkan Pesan Error
end
@enduml